Quote: Writing to his mother, Mrs D. Gordon, from Egypt on January 23 last, Lance Corporal W. Heany said he was still in good health. They expected another big 'slather up', and he was sure they would shatter the Turks and Germans because they had plenty of confidence in themselves.
